Package: NOAAsignif
Type: Package
Title: Visualize significant earthquake dataset from NOAA website
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Qinan Hu 
Maintainer: Qinan Hu <qh78@cornell.edu>
Description: Capstone Project for Coursera's Mastering Software Development with R Specialization.
    This package contains functions that obtain and clean datasets of significant earthquakes from NOAA website.
    It also provides functions to visulize the data in a labeled timeline or interactive map.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: dplyr, ggplot2, leaflet, lubridate, magrittr, readr, stringr, tidyr, rlang
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
